title: Starbomb (2013) Egoraptor & Ninja Sex Party album
description: Starbomb is the eponymous debut studio album by American comedy supergroup Starbomb, composed of Leigh Daniel Avidan (Danny Sexbang) and Brian Wecht of American comedy duo Ninja Sex Party and Flash animator and internet personality Arin Hanson (Egoraptor). Starbomb brings together the sexually provocative music stylings of NSP and the video game-based humor of Egoraptor. The album was released on December 17, 2013.
